  "title": "Area History | Raleigh Hills Business Association",
  "description": "ONE THEORY OF HOW RALEIGH HILLS GOT ITS NAME Raleigh S. Robinson, who is a native of Washington county, now owns and operates a portion of the farm where he was born on the 2nd of May, 1857. His parents were William J. and Emeline (Barnum) Robinson, the father's birth having occurred in Mercer",
  "htmlMain": "<div id=\"pl-675\" class=\"panel-layout\"><div id=\"pg-675-0\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"><div id=\"pgc-675-0-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-675-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child\" data-index=\"0\"><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n\t<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">ONE THEORY OF HOW RALEIGH HILLS GOT ITS NAME</h2>\n<p>Raleigh S. Robinson, who is a native of Washington county, now owns and operates a portion of the farm where he was born on the 2nd of May, 1857. His <a href=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/William_J_Robinson.png\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-13\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/William_J_Robinson-233x300.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/William_J_Robinson-233x300.png 233w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/William_J_Robinson.png 249w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 233px) 100vw, 233px\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>parents were William J. and Emeline (Barnum) Robinson, the father's birth having occurred in Mercer county, Pennsylvania, on the 12th of October, 1827, and that of the mother in Jefferson county, Indiana, on September 16, 1829.<br>They were married in the latter county on the 9th of January, 1848, but began their domestic life in Jennings county, Indiana, where they resided until April, 1851. The children of pioneers, naturally they felt that better opportunities were afforded all young people in a new country, so despite their very limited means and the many hardships and dangers they knew lay before them, they courageously started across the plains to Oregon.<br>The journey was long and tiresome, occupying nearly six months, but in September they arrived in Clackamas county, where they spent six weeks. In the following March Mr. Robinson filed on a donation claim in Washington, county, to which they removed and there spent the remainder of their lives.</p>\n<p>Raleigh Hills seems to be named after Raleigh Robinson. A post office named Raleigh was established in the area April 1892, and was closed twelve years later. Southern Pacific's Red Electric line had a stop in Raleigh from 1914 until the line ceased operation in 1929. A Raleigh Hills branch of the Portland post office was opened in 1968.</p>\n<p>Raleigh Hills is a neighborhood within the metropolitan area of Portland. It is located in the southwest hills in Washington County, bordered by Beaverton to the west, West Slope to the north, with Progress and Garden Home to the south. the population is about 6,000.</p>\n<p>The central area is located at the intersection of Oregon Routes 10 and 210. That is&nbsp; the Beaverton Hillsdale Highway and Scholls Ferry Road intersection:</p>\n\n</div>\n</div></div><div id=\"panel-675-0-0-1\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor\" data-index=\"1\"><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n\t<h2>Check out these links for more information:</h2>\n<h2>First People<img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3397\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Agate-Kalapuyan-Hunter-696x462-1-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Agate-Kalapuyan-Hunter-696x462-1-300x199.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Agate-Kalapuyan-Hunter-696x462-1-100x66.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Agate-Kalapuyan-Hunter-696x462-1-150x100.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Agate-Kalapuyan-Hunter-696x462-1-200x133.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Agate-Kalapuyan-Hunter-696x462-1-450x299.jpg 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Agate-Kalapuyan-Hunter-696x462-1-600x398.jpg 600w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Agate-Kalapuyan-Hunter-696x462-1.jpg 696w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" loading=\"lazy\"></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"bv0rcx7p0Y\"><p><a href=\"https://fiveoaksmuseum.org/this-is-kalapuyan-land-tribes-and-languages-map/\">This IS Kalapuyan Land: Tribes and Languages Map</a></p></blockquote>\n\n<h2>Raleigh Park History - Farmland to Golf Course: The Making of a Neighborhood</h2>\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.raleighparkgardentour.com/a-short-history-of-our-neighborhood.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Raleigh Park Garden Tour</a></h2>\n<h2>Raleigh Hills, Oregon - History, Geography, Demographics, References</h2>\n<h2>Raleigh Hills</h2>\n<h2><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Raleigh_Hills,_Oregon\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">External links&nbsp; &nbsp; <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3552\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Screenshjot-of-BHH-and-Scholls-Ferry-300x261.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Screenshjot-of-BHH-and-Scholls-Ferry-300x261.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Screenshjot-of-BHH-and-Scholls-Ferry-100x87.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Screenshjot-of-BHH-and-Scholls-Ferry-150x131.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Screenshjot-of-BHH-and-Scholls-Ferry-200x174.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Screenshjot-of-BHH-and-Scholls-Ferry.jpg 319w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></h2>\n<h2><a href=\"http://www.pdxhistory.com/index.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PDX History</a> <a href=\"http://www.pdxhistory.com/html/red_electrics.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Red Electrics</a></h2>\n</div>\n</div></div><div id=\"panel-675-0-0-2\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\"><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n\t<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3547\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/The-Red-Image-Southern-Pacific-Lines-300x262.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/The-Red-Image-Southern-Pacific-Lines-300x262.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/The-Red-Image-Southern-Pacific-Lines-768x671.jpg 768w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/The-Red-Image-Southern-Pacific-Lines-100x87.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/The-Red-Image-Southern-Pacific-Lines-150x131.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/The-Red-Image-Southern-Pacific-Lines-200x175.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/The-Red-Image-Southern-Pacific-Lines-450x393.jpg 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/The-Red-Image-Southern-Pacific-Lines-600x524.jpg 600w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/The-Red-Image-Southern-Pacific-Lines.jpg 851w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"></p>\n\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-675-1\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"><div id=\"pgc-675-1-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-675-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\"><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-